data.description:
This house is fully updated, waiting for you to make it your own! Located in a highly desired neighborhood.
Inside, the living room lets in lots of sunlight, which makes it super cozy. The kitchen has a large layout making cooking a breeze. The backyard has plenty of room for relaxing or having a cook out.
It's hard to find a ready to move into home at this price point anymore.
It's close to places like Phalen, with its great walking paths. Plus, this house is all ready for you to move in and start making memories!
